					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">SMC loads from FDS disks, PC and 3.5" disks (hence the file header) but all information regarding the SMC was kept private, it wasn't a very dev friendly solution, every last file was released by FFE themselves. The only way to make your own game files would be to dump FDS based Magic Card games to disk which was a function added to a specific SMC BIOS</div>

